ilog.concert

Interface IloTuple

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IloTupleBuffer

    public interface IloTuple
    This interface represents an IloTuple that is a line of an IloTupleSet (pointed to by the index). You should not create IloTuple objects directly. You should create them using IloTupleSet.makeTuple(int).
    see

    IloTupleSet
